#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1518
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KMyMoney cannot determine which of your accounts to use.  You can create a "
"new account by pressing the <b>Create</b> button or select another one "
"manually from the selection box below."
msgstr ""
"KMyMoney ບໍ່ສາມາດກຳນົດໄດ້ວ່າຈະໃຊ້ບັນຊີໃດຂອງເຈົ້າ. ເຈົ້າສາມາດສ້າງບັນຊີໃໝ່ໄດ້ ໂດຍການກົດປຸ່ມ "
"<b>ສ້າງ</b> ຫຼື ເລືອກບັນຊີອື່ນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງຈາກກ່ອງເລືອກທາງລຸ່ມ."

#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1523
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"No account information has been found in the selected statement file. Please "
"select an account using the selection box in the dialog or create a new "
"account by pressing the <b>Create</b> button."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ພົບຂໍ້ມູນບັນຊີໃນໄຟລ໌ໃບແຈ້ງຍອດທີ່ເລືອກ. ກະລຸນາເລືອກບັນຊີໂດຍໃຊ້ກ່ອງເລືອກໃນໜ້າຕ່າງ ຫຼື "
"ສ້າງບັນຊີໃໝ່ໂດຍການກົດປຸ່ມ <b>ສ້າງ</b>."

#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1552
