#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, m_skipStripping)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsonlinequotes.ui:155
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>For easier processing of the data returned by the online source, KMyMoney "
"usually strips unused parts before it is parsed with the regular "
"expressions. If matching of the fields relies on those items, then use this "
"option to turn stripping off.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>The following items are usually removed by stripping:\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li>HTML tags such as <b>&lt;tag&gt;</b></li>\n"
"<li>& encoded characters such as <b>&amp;nbsp;</b></li>\n"
"<li>duplicate whitespace</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ເພື່ອການປະມວນຜົນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນຈາກແຫຼ່ງອອນລາຍ, KMyMoney "
"ມັກຈະຕັດສ່ວນທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ອອກກ່ອນຈະແຍກດ້ວຍ Regular Expressions. "
"ຖ້າການຈັບຄູ່ຟີວຕ້ອງການລາຍການເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ເພື່ອປິດການຕັດອອກ.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>ລາຍການຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ມັກຈະຖືກຕັດອອກ:\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li>ແທັກ HTML ເຊັ່ນ <b>&lt;tag&gt;</b></li>\n"
"<li>& ຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ເຂົ້າລະຫັດ ເຊັ່ນ <b>&amp;nbsp;</b></li>\n"
"<li>ຍະຫວ່າງທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນ</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"</p>"

