msgid "Do not auto-fill transaction data at all."
msgstr "ບໍ່ຕ້ອງຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນທຸລະກຳອັດຕະໂນມັດເລີຍ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton1)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:403
#, kde-format
msgid "No Autofill"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີການຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton2)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:412
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Collect all transactions for the given payee. Treat all transactions that "
"refer to the same category and have an amount with +/- X % as identical. If "
"more than one transaction is found, a list of them is presented to the "
"user.\n"
"\n"
"Selecting 0% will list all transactions."
msgstr ""
"ເກັບກຳທຸລະກຳທັງໝົດສຳລັບຜູ້ຮັບເງິນທີ່ລະບຸ. ຖືວ່າທຸລະກຳທັງໝົດທີ່ອ້າງອີງເຖິງໝວດໝູ່ດຽວກັນ ແລະ "
"ມີຈຳນວນເງິນພາຍໃນ +/- X % ແມ່ນຄືກັນ. ຖ້າພົບຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງທຸລະກຳ, ລາຍການຈະຖືກນຳສະເໜີໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້.\n"
"\n"
"ການເລືອກ 0% ຈະລາຍຊື່ທຸລະກຳທັງໝົດ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton2)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:415
#, kde-format
msgid "Same transaction if amount differs less than percentage set below"
msgstr "ທຸລະກຳດຽວກັນຖ້າຈຳນວນເງິນແຕກຕ່າງກັນໜ້ອຍກວ່າເປີເຊັນທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ດ້ານລຸ່ມ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton3)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:428
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The data of the last transaction assigned to the category used most often "
"for this payee is autofilled into the transaction editor."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທຸລະກຳລ່າສຸດທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້ກັບໝວດໝູ່ທີ່ໃຊ້ເລື້ອຍທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບຜູ້ຮັບເງິນນີ້ຈະຖືກຕື່ມໃສ່ໃນຕົວແກ້ໄຂທຸລະກຳໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton3)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:431
#, kde-format
msgid "With previously most often used transaction for the payee"
msgstr "ດ້ວຍທຸລະກຳທີ່ໃຊ້ເລື້ອຍທີ່ສຸດກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ສຳລັບຜູ້ຮັບເງິນ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, l4)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:450
#, kde-format
msgid "Same transaction if amount differs less than "
msgstr "ທຸລະກຳດຽວກັນຖ້າຈຳນວນເງິນແຕກຕ່າງກັນໜ້ອຍກວ່າ "

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QSpinBox, kcfg_AutoFillDifference)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:457
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Two transactions are usually treated identical for autofill, if they refer "
"the same accounts. They are treated as different transactions though, when "
"their amount varies by more than the percentage given here."
msgstr ""
"ສອງທຸລະກຳມັກຈະຖືກຖືວ່າຄືກັນສຳລັບການຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ຖ້າພວກມັນອ້າງອີງເຖິງບັນຊີດຽວກັນ. "
"ແຕ່ພວກມັນຈະຖືກຖືວ່າເປັນທຸລະກຳທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ "
"ເມື່ອຈຳນວນເງິນຂອງພວກມັນແຕກຕ່າງກັນຫຼາຍກວ່າເປີເຊັນທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້."

#. i18n: ectx: property (suffix), widget (QSpinBox, kcfg_AutoFillDifference)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:460
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid "%"
msgstr "%"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_AutoFillUseMemos)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:489
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked the memos from the previous transaction will be "
"used otherwise the memos will not be considered when the transaction is "
"autofilled."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເລືອກຕົວເລືອກນີ້ ບັນທຶກຊ່ວຍຈຳຈາກທຸລະກຳກ່ອນໜ້າຈະຖືກນຳມາໃຊ້ "
"ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນບັນທຶກຊ່ວຍຈຳຈະບໍ່ຖືກພິຈາລະນາເມື່ອທຸລະກຳຖືກຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_AutoFillUseMemos)
