#, kde-format
msgid "GPG not found"
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບ GPG"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>You have selected to encrypt your data also with the KMyMoney recover "
"key, but the key with id</p><p><center><b>%1</b></center></p><p>has not been "
"found in your keyring at this time. Please make sure to import this key into "
"your keyring. You can find it on the <a href=\"https://kmymoney.org/"
"\">KMyMoney web-site</a>. This time your data will not be encrypted with the "
"KMyMoney recover key.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ທ່ານໄດ້ເລືອກທີ່ຈະເຂົ້າລະຫັດຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍຄີກູ້ຄືນ KMyMoney, ແຕ່ຄີທີ່ມີ ID</p><p><center><b>"
"%1</b></center></p><p>ບໍ່ພົບໃນພວງຄີຂອງທ່ານໃນເວລານີ້. "
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່ານຳເຂົ້າຄີນີ້ເຂົ້າໄປໃນພວງຄີຂອງທ່ານ. ທ່ານສາມາດຊອກຫາມັນໄດ້ໃນ <a href="
"\"https://kmymoney.org/\">ເວັບໄຊ KMyMoney</a>. "
"ຄັ້ງນີ້ຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານຈະບໍ່ຖືກເຂົ້າລະຫັດດ້ວຍຄີກູ້ຄືນ KMyMoney.</p>"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:128
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:141
#, kde-format
msgid "GPG Key not found"
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບຄີ GPG"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:137
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>You have specified to encrypt your data for the user-id</p><p><center><b>"
"%1</b>.</center></p><p>Unfortunately, a valid key for this user-id was not "
"found in your keyring. Please make sure to import a valid key for this user-"
"id. This time, encryption is disabled.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ທ່ານໄດ້ລະບຸໃຫ້ເຂົ້າລະຫັດຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານສຳລັບ ID ຜູ້ໃຊ້</p><p><center><b>%1</b>.</center></"
"p><p>ໜ້າເສຍດາຍ, ບໍ່ພົບຄີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງສຳລັບ ID ຜູ້ໃຊ້ນີ້ໃນພວງຄີຂອງທ່ານ. "
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່ານຳເຂົ້າຄີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງສຳລັບ ID ຜູ້ໃຊ້ນີ້. ຄັ້ງນີ້, ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານ.</p>"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>You have configured to save your data in encrypted form using GPG. Make "
"sure you understand that you might lose all your data if you encrypt it, but "
"cannot decrypt it later on. If unsure, answer <b>No</b>.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ທ່ານໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ບັນທຶກຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານໃນຮູບແບບເຂົ້າລະຫັດໂດຍໃຊ້ GPG. "
"ກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າທ່ານເຂົ້າໃຈວ່າທ່ານອາດຈະສູນເສຍຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານຖ້າທ່ານເຂົ້າລະຫັດມັນ, "
"ແຕ່ບໍ່ສາມາດຖອດລະຫັດໄດ້ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ. ຖ້າບໍ່ແນ່ໃຈ, ໃຫ້ຕອບ <b>ບໍ່</b>.</p>"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:151
#, kde-format
msgid "Store GPG encrypted"
msgstr "ບັນທຶກແບບເຂົ້າລະຫັດ GPG"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:177
#, kde-format
msgid "Unable to open file '%1' for writing."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດໄຟລ໌ '%1' ເພື່ອຂຽນໄດ້."

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:278
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have configured KMyMoney to use GPG to protect your data and to encrypt "
"your data also with the KMyMoney recover key. This key is about to expire in "
"%1 day. Please update the key from a keyserver using your GPG frontend (e.g. "
"KGPG)."
msgid_plural ""
"You have configured KMyMoney to use GPG to protect your data and to encrypt "
"your data also with the KMyMoney recover key. This key is about to expire in "
"%1 days. Please update the key from a keyserver using your GPG frontend (e."
"g. KGPG)."
msgstr[0] ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າ KMyMoney ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ GPG ເພື່ອປົກປ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເພື່ອເຂົ້າລະຫັດຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍຄີກູ້ຄືນ "
"KMyMoney ເຊັ່ນກັນ. ຄີນີ້ກຳລັງຈະໝົດອາຍຸໃນ %1 ມື້. ກະລຸນາອັບເດດຄີຈາກເຊີບເວີຄີໂດຍໃຊ້ GPG frontend "
"ຂອງທ່ານ (ເຊັ່ນ KGPG)."

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:283
#, kde-format
msgid "Recover key expires soon"
msgstr "ຄີກູ້ຄືນໃກ້ຈະໝົດອາຍຸແລ້ວ"

#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstorage.cpp:358
