msgstr "ສີພື້ນຫຼັງສໍາລັບທຸລະກຳທີ່ນໍາເຂົ້າ"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (transactionImportedText), group (Color Options)
#: kmymoney/settings/kmymoney.kcfg:206
#, kde-format
