msgstr "ສີຂໍ້ຄວາມສໍາລັບທຸລະກຳທີ່ນໍາເຂົ້າ"

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (transactionMatchedColor), group (Color Options)
#: kmymoney/settings/kmymoney.kcfg:210
#, kde-format
