#: kmymoney/views/reconciliationledgerviewpage.cpp:124
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KMyMoney has detected transactions matching your reconciliation data.\n"
"Would you like KMyMoney to clear these transactions for you?"
msgstr ""
"KMyMoney ກວດພົບທຸລະກຳທີ່ກົງກັບຂໍ້ມູນການປັບຍອດຂອງທ່ານ.\n"
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ KMyMoney ເຄລຍທຸລະກຳເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໃຫ້ທ່ານບໍ່?"

#: kmymoney/views/reconciliationledgerviewpage.cpp:256
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You are about to finish the reconciliation of this account with a difference "
"between your bank statement and the transactions marked as cleared.\n"
"Are you sure you want to finish the reconciliation?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານກຳລັງຈະສຳເລັດການປັບຍອດຂອງບັນຊີນີ້ ໂດຍມີຜົນຕ່າງລະຫວ່າງໃບແຈ້ງຍອດທະນາຄານຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ "
"ທຸລະກຳທີ່ໝາຍວ່າເຄລຍແລ້ວ.\n"
"ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອງການສຳເລັດການປັບຍອດ?"

#: kmymoney/views/reconciliationledgerviewpage.cpp:259
#, kde-format
msgid "Confirm end of reconciliation"
msgstr "ຢືນຢັນການສິ້ນສຸດການປັບຍອດ"

