#: kmymoney/views/simpleledgerview.cpp:406
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"The close button for this account has been removed because you are "
"reconciling it. Finish, cancel or postpone the reconciliation to get it back."
msgstr ""
"ປຸ່ມປິດສຳລັບບັນຊີນີ້ຖືກລົບອອກ ເພາະວ່າທ່ານກຳລັງປັບຍອດມັນຢູ່. ໃຫ້ສຳເລັດ, ຍົກເລີກ ຫຼື "
"ເລື່ອນການປັບຍອດອອກໄປກ່ອນ ເພື່ອເອົາມັນກັບຄືນມາ."

#: kmymoney/views/simpleledgerview.cpp:517
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label displayed when no ledger is open"
msgid ""
"This page shows the accounts ledger. Currently, no accounts exist so this "
"text is shown instead."
msgstr "ໜ້ານີ້ສະແດງບັນຊີແຍກປະເພດ. ປັດຈຸບັນ, ບໍ່ມີບັນຊີຢູ່ເລີຍ ດັ່ງນັ້ນຂໍ້ຄວາມນີ້ຈຶ່ງສະແດງຂຶ້ນມາແທນ."

#: kmymoney/views/simpleledgerview.cpp:520
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label displayed when no ledger is open"
msgid ""
"This page shows the accounts ledger. Currently, no accounts are selected so "
"this text is shown instead."
msgstr "ໜ້ານີ້ສະແດງບັນຊີແຍກປະເພດ. ປັດຈຸບັນ, ບໍ່ມີບັນຊີຖືກເລີຍ ດັ່ງນັ້ນຂໍ້ຄວາມນີ້ຈຶ່ງສະແດງຂຶ້ນມາແທນ."

