#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel16)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kcreditcardschedulepage.ui:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"For credit card accounts you can create a monthly schedule which will "
