msgstr "ປະເພດຂອງເງິນກູ້ແມ່ນຫຍັງ?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_borrowButton)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_loanDirection)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:45
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/lendborrowwizardpage.ui:68
#, kde-format
msgid "I am borrowing money"
msgstr "ຂ້ອຍກຳລັງຢືມເງິນ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_lendButton)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_loanDirection)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:50
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/lendborrowwizardpage.ui:78
#, kde-format
msgid "I am lending money"
msgstr "ຂ້ອຍກຳລັງໃຫ້ຢືມເງິນ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:58
#, kde-format
msgid "Who is the payee/payer of the loan?"
msgstr "ໃຜແມ່ນຜູ້ຮັບ/ຜູ້ຈ່າຍເງິນກູ້?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyPayeeCombo, m_payee)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the person or bank you owe money or who owes you money.\n"
"\n"
"If the name does not exist within KMyMoney's database, you are asked if you "
"want to create it."
msgstr ""
"ປ້ອນຊື່ຂອງບຸກຄົນ ຫຼື ທະນາຄານທີ່ທ່ານຕິດໜີ້ ຫຼື ຜູ້ທີ່ຕິດໜີ້ທ່ານ.\n"
"\n"
"ຖ້າຊື່ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງ KMyMoney, ທ່ານຈະຖືກຖາມວ່າຕ້ອງການສ້າງມັນຫຼືບໍ່."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Did you make/receive any payments yet?"
msgstr "ທ່ານໄດ້ຈ່າຍ/ຮັບການຊຳລະເງິນແລ້ວຫຼືຍັງ?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KComboBox, m_anyPayments)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:89
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Were there any payments for this loan whether they are entered into KMyMoney "
"or not?\n"
"\n"
"Note: Payments made to obtain the loan (e.g. Disagio) are not considered as "
"payments in this context."
msgstr ""
"ມີການຊຳລະເງິນສຳລັບເງິນກູ້ນີ້ຫຼືບໍ່ ບໍ່ວ່າພວກມັນຈະຖືກປ້ອນເຂົ້າໃນ KMyMoney ແລ້ວຫຼືຍັງ?\n"
"\n"
"ໝາຍເຫດ: ການຊຳລະເງິນເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ເງິນກູ້ (ເຊັ່ນ: Disagio) "
"ບໍ່ຖືກພິຈາລະນາວ່າເປັນການຊຳລະເງິນໃນບໍລິບົດນີ້."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_anyPayments)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:93
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item no payments were entered for a loan"
msgid "No"
msgstr "ບໍ່"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_anyPayments)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:98
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item payments were entered for a loan"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "ແມ່ນ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:106
#, kde-format
msgid "Which payments do you want to record?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການບັນທຶກການຊຳລະເງິນໃດ?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KComboBox, m_recordings)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:121
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>Select which transactions should be recorded.\n"
"\n"
"<b>All payments</b> allows you to enter all payments made for this loan.\n"
"\n"
"The option to <b>start from the beginning of the current year</b> is meant "
"for loans that have already been active for a longer period of time, and for "
"which you do not want to enter all past transactions.\n"
"</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>ເລືອກທຸລະກຳທີ່ຄວນບັນທຶກ.\n"
"\n"
"<b>ການຊຳລະເງິນທັງໝົດ</b> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານປ້ອນການຊຳລະເງິນທັງໝົດທີ່ເຮັດສຳລັບເງິນກູ້ນີ້.\n"
"\n"
"ຕົວເລືອກ <b>ເລີ່ມຈາກຕົ້ນປີປັດຈຸບັນ</b> ແມ່ນສຳລັບເງິນກູ້ທີ່ມີການເຄື່ອນໄຫວດົນນານມາແລ້ວ, "
"ແລະທ່ານບໍ່ຕ້ອງການປ້ອນທຸລະກຳທີ່ຜ່ານມາທັງໝົດ.\n"
"</qt>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_recordings)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:125
#, kde-format
msgid "All payments"
msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນທັງໝົດ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_recordings)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:130
#, kde-format
msgid "Start with this year's payments"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງປີນີ້"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:138
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the ending balance found on the statement that is the last one before "
"you want to start recording this loan in KMyMoney."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຍອດຍົກໄປທີ່ພົບໃນໃບແຈ້ງຍອດທີ່ເປັນໃບສຸດທ້າຍກ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຈະເລີ່ມບັນທຶກເງິນກູ້ນີ້ໃນ KMyMoney."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:141
#, kde-format
msgid "Balance before start of recording"
msgstr "ຍອດເງິນກ່ອນເລີ່ມການບັນທຶກ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (AmountEdit, m_openingBalance)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:151
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have selected to record only payments from the beginning of this year. "
"Since prior transactions will not be recorded, you need to supply the "
"balance of the loan on January 1st of this year."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ເລືອກບັນທຶກສະເພາະການຊຳລະເງິນຕັ້ງແຕ່ຕົ້ນປີນີ້. ເນື່ອງຈາກທຸລະກຳກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ຈະບໍ່ຖືກບັນທຶກ, "
"ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງລະບຸຍອດເງິນກູ້ໃນວັນທີ 1 ມັງກອນ ຂອງປີນີ້."

#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWizardPage, PaymentFrequencyWizardPage)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel5)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:158
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/paymentfrequencywizardpage.ui:6
#, kde-format
msgid "Payment frequency"
msgstr "ຄວາມຖີ່ການຊຳລະ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_4)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:175
#, kde-format
msgid "Interest Compounding frequency"
msgstr "ຄວາມຖີ່ການຄິດດອກເບ້ຍທົບຕົ້ນ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyFrequencyCombo, m_compoundFrequency)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:185
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Select the frequency with which the interest is compounded. If uncertain, "
"select the same as the payment frequency. Consult your loan contract for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກຄວາມຖີ່ທີ່ດອກເບ້ຍຈະຖືກຄິດທົບຕົ້ນ. ຖ້າບໍ່ແນ່ໃຈ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຄືກັນກັບຄວາມຖີ່ການຊຳລະ. "
"ປຶກສາສັນຍາເງິນກູ້ຂອງທ່ານສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:192
#, kde-format
msgid "Due date of first payment to be recorded"
msgstr "ວັນຄົບກຳນົດຂອງການຊຳລະເງິນຄັ້ງທຳອິດທີ່ຈະບັນທຶກ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyDateEdit, m_firstPaymentDate)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:211
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the answer to <b>What do you want to record?</b> this field "
"means the following:<p>\n"
"\n"
"<b>All payments</b><br>\n"
"Enter the due date of the very first payment<p>\n"
"\n"
"<b>Start with this year's payments</b><br>\n"
"Enter the due date of the first payment in the current year"
msgstr ""
"ຂຶ້ນກັບຄຳຕອບຂອງ <b>ທ່ານຕ້ອງການບັນທຶກຫຍັງ?</b> ຊ່ອງນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າດັ່ງນີ້:<p>\n"
"\n"
"<b>ການຊຳລະເງິນທັງໝົດ</b><br>\n"
"ປ້ອນວັນຄົບກຳນົດຂອງການຊຳລະເງິນຄັ້ງທຳອິດສຸດ<p>\n"
"\n"
"<b>ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງປີນີ້</b><br>\n"
"ປ້ອນວັນຄົບກຳນົດຂອງການຊຳລະເງິນຄັ້ງທຳອິດໃນປີປັດຈຸບັນ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel4)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:218
#, kde-format
msgid "Type of interest rate"
msgstr "ປະເພດຂອງອັດຕາດອກເບ້ຍ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_interestType)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:229
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item type of interest"
msgid "Fixed"
msgstr "ຄົງທີ່"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_interestType)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:234
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item type of interest"
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້"

