msgstr "ການປ່ຽນແປງດອກເບ້ຍຄັ້ງຖັດໄປແມ່ນຮອດກຳນົດ"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/khierarchypage.cpp:152
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info Missing parent account selection in new account wizard"
msgid "No parent account selected"
msgstr "ບໍ່ໄດ້ເລືອກບັນຊີຫຼັກ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/khierarchypage.ui:26
#, kde-format
