msgstr "KMyMoney ໄດ້ຄິດໄລ່ອັດຕາດອກເບ້ຍເປັນ %1%."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:197
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:323
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KMyMoney has calculated a periodic payment of %1 to cover principal and "
