"The number of payments has been decremented and the balloon payment has been "
"modified to %1."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນງວດການຊຳລະຖືກຫຼຸດລົງ ແລະ ການຊຳລະເງິນກ້ອນສຸດທ້າຍຖືກແກ້ໄຂເປັນ %1."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:215
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:232
#, kde-format
msgid "The balloon payment has been modified to %1."
msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນກ້ອນສຸດທ້າຍຖືກແກ້ໄຂເປັນ %1."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:226
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:352
#, kde-format
