msgstr "KMyMoney ໄດ້ຄິດໄລ່ໄລຍະເວລາຂອງເງິນກູ້ຂອງທ່ານເປັນ %1. "

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:262
#, kde-format
msgid "KMyMoney has calculated a balloon payment of %1 for this loan."
msgstr "KMyMoney ໄດ້ຄິດໄລ່ການຊຳລະເງິນກ້ອນສຸດທ້າຍເປັນ %1 ສຳລັບເງິນກູ້ນີ້."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:268
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:396
#, kde-format
msgid "KMyMoney has successfully verified your loan information."
msgstr "KMyMoney ໄດ້ກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນເງິນກູ້ຂອງທ່ານສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:275
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have entered mis-matching information. Please modify your figures or "
"leave one value empty to let KMyMoney calculate it for you"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ບໍ່ກົງກັນ. ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂຕົວເລກຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ປະຄ່າໜຶ່ງວ່າງໄວ້ເພື່ອໃຫ້ KMyMoney ຄິດໄລ່ໃຫ້ທ່ານ"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.cpp:278
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:109
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:116
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:123
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:131
