#, kde-format
msgid "Enter additional fees"
msgstr "ປ້ອນຄ່າທຳນຽມເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/additionalfeeswizardpage.cpp:45
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Use this to add any additional fees other than principal and interest "
"contained in your periodical payments."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ອັນນີ້ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຄ່າທຳນຽມເພີ່ມເຕີມນອກເໜືອຈາກເງິນຕົ້ນແລະດອກເບ້ຍ ທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນການຊຳລະເງິນເປັນງວດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel21_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/additionalfeeswizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"If your regular payment contains any additional fees, click on the button "
"\"Additional fees\" to enter them."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ຖ້າການຊຳລະປົກກະຕິຂອງທ່ານມີຄ່າທຳນຽມເພີ່ມເຕີມ, ໃຫ້ຄິກທີ່ປຸ່ມ \"ຄ່າທຳນຽມເພີ່ມເຕີມ\" ເພື່ອປ້ອນພວກມັນ."

