#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWizardPage, CalculationOverviewWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/calculationoverviewwizardpage.ui:6
#, kde-format
msgid "Calculation Overview"
msgstr "ພາບລວມການຄິດໄລ່"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel18_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/calculationoverviewwizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"KMyMoney has calculated the loan as shown in the overview below. You can "
"accept these values by selecting \"Next\" or change them by choosing \"Back"
"\" to return to the input field for the information you want to change."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"KMyMoney ໄດ້ຄິດໄລ່ເງິນກູ້ຕາມທີ່ສະແດງໃນພາບລວມຂ້າງລຸ່ມນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດຍອມຮັບຄ່າເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກ "
"\"ຖັດໄປ\" ຫຼື ປ່ຽນພວກມັນໂດຍການເລືອກ \"ກັບຄືນ\" "
"ເພື່ອກັບຄືນໄປຫາຊ່ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນ."

