#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel15_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/durationwizardpage.ui:13
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please enter the term of this loan or leave the field empty to calculate it. "
"The term is the time that is required to fully repay the loan. This time "
"might be different from the time your loan contract is signed for."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ກະລຸນາປ້ອນໄລຍະເວລາຂອງເງິນກູ້ນີ້ ຫຼື ປ່ອຍຊ່ອງວ່າງໄວ້ເພື່ອຄິດໄລ່ມັນ. "
"ໄລຍະເວລາແມ່ນເວລາທີ່ຕ້ອງການເພື່ອຊຳລະຄືນເງິນກູ້ໃຫ້ໝົດ. "
"ເວລານີ້ອາດຈະແຕກຕ່າງຈາກເວລາທີ່ສັນຍາເງິນກູ້ຂອງທ່ານລະບຸໄວ້."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel1_1_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editintrowizardpage.ui:43
#, kde-format
msgid "Edit Loan Account Wizard"
msgstr "ວິດຊາດແກ້ໄຂບັນຊີເງິນກູ້"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel1_2_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editintrowizardpage.ui:77
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Welcome to the Edit Loan Account Wizard. Please use this wizard to modify "
"information about your loan account.\n"
"\n"
"Please make sure that you have the relevant information handy. You usually "
"get the information out of your contract and the last statement."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ວິດຊາດແກ້ໄຂບັນຊີເງິນກູ້. ກະລຸນາໃຊ່ວິດຊາດນີ້ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບບັນຊີເງິນກູ້ຂອງທ່ານ.\n"
"\n"
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າທ່ານມີຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຢູ່ໃນມື. ປົກກະຕິແລ້ວທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຂໍ້ມູນຈາກສັນຍາ ແລະ "
"ໃບແຈ້ງຍອດຫຼ້າສຸດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QWizardPage, EditSelectionWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Edit selection"
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂການເລືອກ"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel2_2_1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:27
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please select, which data of the loan you want to modify."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ກະລຸນາເລືອກ ຂໍ້ມູນຂອງເງິນກູ້ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂ."

